															How to Login to the OpenCart 1.5 Dashboard									</h1>
			
																
				
					<div style='font-size:12px; color:#aaa; margin-bottom:-10px; padding-top:5px;'>
							<div style='float:left; margin-right:20px;'><span style='color:#606060;'>Written by </span><a href='https://plus.google.com/u/0/114162951489960418846?rel=author'>John-Paul Briones</a></div>
							<div style='float:left; margin-right:20px;'><span style='color:#606060;'>Views:</span> <span name='page_views' id='page_views'>28,647</span></div>
							<div style='float:left; margin-right:20px;' title='Originally published: Mar 18, 2014'><span style='color:#606060;'>Published:</span> Apr 22, 2016</div>
							<div style='float:left; margin-right:20px;'><span style='color:#606060;'>Comments:</span> <a href='#comments'>22</a></div>
